metadata.name: ⋄⊱Darier⊰⋄
metadata.description:
I was like in a dream. I started seeing all the colors I love. I saw so many colors that my eyes began to deceive me. Everything was getting mixed up and I was starting to see blurry. I began to fall into the void and continued to watch my hands. There was something I wanted to shout out, but I didn't know what it was.

6000x5000px
300dpi
Digital Painting
